IEvent - Interface in marge.middleware.shared.event.specification
This is an interface of Event
IEventType - Interface in marge.middleware.shared.event.specification
This class is an interface of EventType
IListener - Interface in marge.middleware.listener.specification
This is an interface that takes a role as subscriber
It will receive IEvent sent by IPublisher and then forward these IEvent to Observer list
IListenerFactory - Interface in marge.middleware.listener.factory.specification
This is an interface that defines methods to create IListener and IPublisher
IListenerFactoryAdaptee - Interface in marge.middleware.listener.factory.specification
This is an interface that adapts between IListenerFactory and its implementation
IPublisher - Interface in marge.middleware.publisher.specification
This class is an interface to define the methods to add subscriber
connect and retrieve data of reader and smart card
The data and events will be collected and are publisher to all subscriber via EventBus
IView - Interface in marge.middleware.listener.view.specification
This class is an interface View to display the data sent IListener
